title: Morning Joe 10/11/21
description: The White House on Friday formally blocked an attempt by former President Donald Trump to withhold documents from Congress related to the Jan. 6 attack on the Capitol, setting up a legal showdown between the current and former presidents over executive privilege.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
